snippet.title: CAT WORLD for Playdate - Chapters 1+2 Trailer
snippet.description:
https://pawprints.games/cat-world

Find your way out of a mysterious forest in CAT WORLD, a narrative puzzle-adventure game for Playdate. You play as Ember, a lost kitten making their way across a strange land, loosely based off sketches I made as a kid.

#indiegames #playdate
